<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Instructions</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script&family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-top: 140px;
            margin-left: 250px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 235, 235, 0.9);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .inst {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .inst h1 {
            font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .inst p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .start {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .start a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
        }

        .start a:hover {
            background: goldenrod;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .bg-video {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            z-index: 1;
            opacity: 0.5; /* Adjust the opacity to make the video less distracting */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <video class="bg-video" autoplay loop muted>
        <source src="../static/bgvInstructions.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        Your browser does not support the video tag.
    </video>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="inst">
            <h1>Instructions</h1>
            <p>Welcome to the quiz! Before you start, please read the following instructions carefully:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Read each question thoroughly before answering.</li>
                <li>Each question has multiple choice answers, choose the correct one.</li>
                <li>There is a time limit for each question, so answer quickly.</li>
                <li>Click "Next" to proceed to the next question.</li>
                <li>You can review your answers at the end of the quiz.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="start">
            <a href="/science">Click To Start</a>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
